
This program gives the required prompts for the user to carry all the functions.
It does all the tasks asked in the project requirements , accept it does not give accomodation for a scheduled calender for different bread orders for different week days, It also does not give a planned itinerary for the delivery.
It facilitates for creating, deleting/modifying breads, ingredients, quantity of breads and ingredients, orders, subscription, recipe


It took approx. 3-4 (504-672) weeks to finish coding and 2-3 hours to finish for submission 
List of challenges

-creating the designing and constantly changing it
-selection of data structures
-reading the xml files
-how to store the data and where to store the data
-writing tests 
-judging the requirements of user
-connection between two classes and their functions